headline: REALIZE Demo Day to Spotlight Health Tech Startups with Expert Insights and Investor Feedback
summary: University Lab Partners (ULP) will host the REALIZE Demo Day on Wednesday, September 17, 2025, from 5:00–8:00 PM PT at UCI Beall Applied Innovation at the Cove. The event marks the capstone of the REALIZE Accelerator program, showcasing live pitch presentations from 11 pioneering med tech startups developing breakthroughs in medical devices, diagnostics, and digital health.
